$grp PS_MissionDescription : "{3136BE42592F3B1B}PrefabsEditable/MissionDescription/EditableMissionDescription.et" {
 {
  coords 1654.786 227.483 728.793
  m_sTitle "SITUATION"
  m_sTextData "<b>Date:</b> 2025-05-04"\
  "<b>Location:</b> Kunar Province, Afghanistan"\
  ""\
  "U.S. Army forces are currently engaged against a newly formed radical offshoot of a known terrorist organization operating within the region. This group has demonstrated increased coordination and tactical capability compared to previous insurgent elements."\
  ""\
  "<b>Recent intelligence confirms the enemy has begun employing:</b>"\
  ""\
  "- Small drones for surveillance and targeting."\
  ""\
  "- Coordinated light infantry assaults, ussually supported by stolen or makeshift APC and gun trucks."\
  ""\
  "As part of a wider battalion-level operation to reestablish presence and deny insurgent freedom of movement in the Kunar region, an understrength U.S. Army Infantry Platoon has reoccupied OP Dallas."\
  ""\
  "Reports indicate enemy forces are massing near the town of Ali Abad. Assessment suggests preparation for a deliberate attack against friendly positions at OP Dallas within the coming hours."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
 }
 {
  coords 1750.552 211.548 815.943
  m_sTitle "MISSION"
  m_sTextData "<b>Defend OP Dallas and eliminate attacking enemy forces.</b>"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 {
  coords 1720.763 219.755 804.214
  m_sTitle "EXECUTION"
  m_sTextData "As per CO's intent."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 {
  coords 1765.292 210.283 814.927
  m_sTitle "ADMIN & LOGISTICS"
  m_sTextData "Soldiers are equipped with their standart combat load."\
  ""\
  "During the previous pullback from the region some construction supplies were left behind at OP Dallas:"\
  ""\
  "- 200 Plastic sandbags"\
  ""\
  "A small cache of weapons, captured during a recent patrol:"\
  ""\
  "- 2x AK-47 rifles"\
  "- <b>2x Remington 870 shotguns </b>"\
  "- 1x VZ-58V rifle"\
  "- 3x M-112 Demolition blocks"\
  "- 1x M-34 Blasting machine"\
  "- Ammunition for the afformentioned weapons."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 5
 }
 {
  coords 1769.902 210.002 823.14
  m_sTitle "FRIENDLY FORCES"
  m_sTextData "Higher headquarters continues offensive operations elsewhere in the province. Immediate reinforcement is limited due to ongoing commitments across the AO."\
  ""\
  "Adjacent friendly units are operating outside immediate supporting distance. "
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 {
  coords 1769.72 209.388 822.603
  m_sTitle "ENEMY FORCES"
  m_sTextData "Enemy strength is estimated to be at around a platoon-sized element."\
  ""\
  "Earlier reports indicate that they possess a stolen APC and limited mortar support."\
  ""\
  "<b>Enemy is know to use small reconnaissance and IED drones.</b>"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 {
  coords 1769.693 209.397 822.506
  m_sTitle "EW CAPABILITIES"
  m_sTextData "Battalion has provided us with a singular static drone jammer located inside the Comand Post."\
  ""\
  "Combat reports show that while effective at interfering with drone signals, <b>the jammers are unable to completely nullify the drone threat.</b>"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 6
 }
}
